objects.name: TitleExplainText
objects.string: It's time to reclaim your freedom...

content.text: It's time to reclaim your freedom...

objects.name: ContentExplainText
objects.string:
You’ve finally made up your mind to leave… Leave for what? You don’t know, but you’re doing it anyway.
It has been snowing for weeks. You would have loved to take your sled, but it’s been broken since your last run...
So, skis it is.

You begin your descent, but after only a few minutes, a deep, thunderous rumble echoes behind you — an avalanche!

Hurry! Run! Run to finally be free…

objects.string:
- Hit the ramps to go faster.


- Avoid the obstacles in your path.


- Don’t get caught by the avalanche!


- Reach the bottom of the mountain and reclaim your freedom.
